title: Bobby Recaps Stories from our iHeartRadio Music Festival + Jimmie Allen on Feelings Going into DWTS Premiere + Jameson Rogers Reveals the Coolest Wedding Gift from a Country Artist
itunes:title: Bobby Recaps Stories from our iHeartRadio Music Festival + Jimmie Allen on Feelings Going into DWTS Premiere + Jameson Rogers Reveals the Coolest Wedding Gift from a Country Artist
description:
Bobby, Amy and Lunchbox share stories from Vegas after spending the weekend at our iHeartRadio Music Festival. We talk to Jimmie Allen who is competing tonight on Dancing with the Stars about how he’s feeling going into the premiere + his CMA nomination for Best New Artist. We also talked to Jameson Rogers about his new album, wedding and the coolest gift he was given by another artist will blow your mind.
